examples.en: We try to match your desires with our possibilities.
Detector is one that finds out what another desires to hide.
He satisfies his desires freely when he can and starves when he is flat.
She desires to remain neutral in the dispute.
He's only concerned with gratifying his own desires.
Men seek for money as the complement of all their desires.
Some medieval monks believed it was necessary to flagellate themselves in order to keep their desires in check...
